ðŸ“˜ Quick Reference â€“ Comparable vs Comparator
Feature	            Comparable	                    Comparator
Location	        Inside the class (implements)	External (passed as argument)
Method	            compareTo()	                    compare()
Purpose	            Natural ordering	            Custom ordering
Used by	            sort(), TreeSet, TreeMap	    Same + thenComparing() etc.
Can sort by field	Only one	                    Multiple (with thenComparing())